citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:23:04.000Z","msg":"去祖記一定變新派路"},{"pid":"a70a23f7bc578cb53db4b6a5182cc99644376c11","tid":2076250,"uid":336453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"踢中堅入過FIFA最佳11人"},{"pid":"dc9e84de64bad5bafd86ad923670f225c8c060bc","tid":2076250,"uid":34572,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"半個都市傳說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防中要嘅位置感唔會俾中堅少，一個成日輕出，又成日忽撚咗唔知走咗走邊個球員點打呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />惟一有得J下嘅所謂長傳，要知道中堅喺全隊第二後嘅位同喺中圈附近嘅壓逼已經唔同啦，佢踢中堅俾佢咁多時間慢慢睇著嚟傳，推上一格一攞波就有人拍，仲點有咁多啲長傳呀講真。<br />\n<br />\n係，喺肥賓時期雷斯係打過幾埸防中，但首先要考慮到佢後面有個泰利，隔離有件林伯，兩個大佬喺度震著佢唔俾佢亂嚟，佢咪少啲衝出嚟柒嘅行為囉，就算柒咗，後面都仲有泰利同卡希爾幫佢執屎，驚閪咩。同埋真係踢得幾埸，對手未熟路好正常，試下長期咁打，對面搵人盯實佢已經廢晒佢武功啦，踢條柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b258a9d1580f3ec277b1c4c6d825aa38ef552db","tid":2076250,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2a546ff4da5d4852b85d689b6ad0f3fd1de04371","tid":2076250,"uid":65386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:22:12.000Z","msg":"車仔有期咪打過一排防中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本唔掂 幫波 控制節奏無瓣得先扔返佢落中堅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"後面有泰利同卡希爾，咪叫做塞多件雷斯當半個中堅，俾林伯，甚至拉美利斯可以更專心攻囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917006c460c012994a084795f757100b